<title>WILLTHERE BE ANY STARS?</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Tunin van gam hawihtak chanchin chuh ka ngaihtuoh,
 Nitum tienga ka tunna ding chuh;
 Lungsiet zala Hukdampa kawm ka tun tieng leh,
 Chawih-atna kei dingin a um dem?

[V2]
 Chawih-atna kei dingin a um dem, a um dem?
 Nitaka nisa a tum tieng leh!
 Chawlhna In nuoma tatsate kawm ka tun tieng,
 Chawih-atna kei dingin a um dem?

[V3]
 2. Lalpa hatna mangin paucham kawmin sem ka,
 Thagau mangthaite chuh man dingin;
 Ni lopi a A chawihatna givel laka,
 Chawih-atna kei din a um theihna'n.

[V4]
 3. Aw, A mel ka muh tiengleh kipak mah mah ka,
 Mangthaite A kawma ka puih chun;
 Sana khawpi a ka kipahna kimna din,
 Chawih-atna kei dingin um ta'n a.</lyrics>
</song>